data.description: Come and see this beautiful 3 bedrooms (one with large walkin closet) and 1.5 bath home.  Completely repainted with all new flooring through out the house.   Brand new A/C Unit!  Large country style kitchen plus a formal dining room with decorative chair railing and crown molding.  One bath up and one bath up.  Large basement with washer & dryer hookup and plenty of room for storage and a work shop.  Large rear yard completely fenced in with rear and front gates.   Rear alley access too!  Very large rear trex decking to sit out and enjoy the beautiful large yard!!  Enjoy the outdoors on the front and side wrap around porch with roses and flowering trees and bushes.  Definitely worth the look with all the extras!!!
